Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.17,0:00:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(182,348)\fnImpact\fax-0.5\fscy200\fscx150\fs38\shad0\1c&H25279A&\3c&HC0C0C0&\3a&HD0&\b1}Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.32,0:00:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up! Set Up! Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gin no kamen ni kuro mafuraa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A mask of silver and a black muffler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hitai ni kagayaku Bui to Bui
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,V and V shining on his forehead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Sutoppu! Goddo no waru-dakumi」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stop GOD's conspiracy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no sakebi wa nami no oto
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,His father's scream is the sound of the waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ikari no Raidoru hikinuite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Furiously drawing the Ridol
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa kyou mo yuku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider comes again today
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X! X! X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke, who was killed by the \Ngreat organization GOD along with his father...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...revived as Kamen Rider X, thanks to his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.55,0:01:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Keisuke's lover, Ryouko, side with GOD?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.01,0:01:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And who is Kiriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.34,0:01:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who fights against the mysterious GOD, Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Assassination Dark Spider Operation!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.62,0:01:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:01:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where's Ryouko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman will soon become a part of GOD as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.60,0:02:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where did she go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.01,0:02:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke. GOD won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.88,0:02:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.41,0:02:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Call number 4. Call number 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Haneda Airport at 13 o'clock. Haneda Airport at 13 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know what GOD's plan is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.21,0:02:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Haneda Airport at 13 o'clock, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,5 more minutes left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll get proof that he's a member of the GOD organization!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Interpol investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you've followed me all the way from the country of Adabu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard, you're a part of GOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,For what reason have you come to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Envoy Kibara of Adabu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,...has come to Japan in order to sign an oil export agreement...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...and is currently staying at the New Japan Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.00,0:03:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That Envoy Kibara will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.79,0:03:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you know this secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Modified human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. My name is Hercules!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.81,0:04:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hercules?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.82,0:04:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Poisonous spiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him, poisonous spiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him, kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You were looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You were looking, weren't you, little girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Meeting you so early is such a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This superhuman powered Hercules shall erase you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just an appetizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time we meet, you'll be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What does Hercules want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Maybe this girl knows something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No use.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, I'm scared! I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.19,0:05:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayoko, it's alright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need for you to be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What did that monster do? Could you please tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayoko. Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'll kill a famous foreigner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to kill a famous foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Sayoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Remeber.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.77,0:06:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember! Kibara! He said it's Kibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sayoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I did tell you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That the next time we meet will be your last!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Set Up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.72,0:07:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridol Stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with your power, trying to break that is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider, look below that bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move, Rider! \NG.O.D has seen through everything already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cook you slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,See that? The last of Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Contact from G.O.D General Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Envoy Kibara is at the New Japan Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hercules. Kidnap the envoy at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to rescue the hostages...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How will GOD contact me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.10,0:11:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kiriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,G.O.D has targeted your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Always be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you know about GOD?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.62,0:11:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell you anything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.88,0:11:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to meet Envoy Kibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Envoy Kibara is in the Hamari Shrine right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamari Shrine, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Envoy Kibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.30,0:12:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want that important body of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The GOD organization wishes to remove\N every single drop of oil from Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I need you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that, Japan will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't resist anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told to press this button...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...in an emergency situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that signal just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Envoy Kibara has been captured by GOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew all along?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke. Don't underestimate the GOD organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll stop your breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Hercules!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Become the seaweed of the sea! Disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Jin Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.61,0:14:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If I fall here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...everything I've done up to now will be useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to follow them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This wonderful place shall be your grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...love Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:15:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't destroy Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.93,0:16:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act so tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you gasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready to execute him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Execute me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All those who object to the GOD organization, \Nregardless of who they are, shall die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to die, then do as we command.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.92,0:16:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ready for his execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.26,0:16:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch carefully, envoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the strongest of cars will be done in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Become a small lump of iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,See.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of sin do they possess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who possesses sin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you resist...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...then those two will need to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready to execute them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.99,0:17:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll agree to your conditions!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.78,0:18:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop! I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Envoy Kibara!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do as he says!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that voice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, X Rider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,X, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hercules! Hercules! Hercules! Hercules!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hercules, here I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away, the three of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are... but thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.48,0:20:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Die...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't move now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,X Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How did you know where I was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You made it look as if you melted into the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But you hit your body on the car...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.70,0:21:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...and by using the recoil, you moved the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:21:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't make optical illusions in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hercules. Do you now understand my strength?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I underestimated you. I lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.25,0:22:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,However, GOD will definitely defeat you one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.61,0:22:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! My power!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...X Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at my death!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:22:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider X won this battle between him and Hercules.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the fearful powers of GOD will target Japan once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.28,0:23:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Kamen Rider X!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.12,0:23:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(462,470)\fad(0,850)\fs38}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.58,0:23:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194,72)\fad(0,10)\fs38}Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode:\N"GOD, the Shadow of Fear!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.50,0:23:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X, X Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no tsukutta Kaizoogu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.81,0:23:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A Kaizorg created by my father
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.22,0:23:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tetsu yori tsuyoi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.22,0:23:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stronger than iron
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oto yori hayai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Faster than sound
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu masuku paafekutaa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,X's mask, Perfecter
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Chichi no negai ga ore no chi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's wishes are in my blood
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}「Warui yatsura ni makeru na to」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.72,0:24:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't lose to those villains!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.64,0:24:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sakende iru ze
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.64,0:24:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He screams
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.90,0:24:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Itsu made mo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.90,0:24:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.15,0:24:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ore wa Ekkusu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.15,0:24:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I am X
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ekkusu Raidaa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.24,0:24:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,X Rider